short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Redirect new tab to a cool website!

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The internet is huge. So many URLs, so many things to see, but the majority of internet users only stay on the big websites without giving the small guys a shot! Support small websites and use Webber to explore the web.

Each time you open a new tab Webber will redirect you to a website that you should totally check out.
